Class MP3File

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uga.cs1302.mp3files.MP3File

  • public class MP3File
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class MP3File, an MP3 class object represents the information about a single MP3 file on a disk. It can also play the MP3 file
